{"tid":1094271,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［統計］今年比沒事巴言論影響過既巴打請進","createTime":"2019-04-06T07:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T08:51:51.000Z","uid":60338,"like":36,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"758e32f90f8b6f30e6fc40a2d1d920b8c40c142c","tid":1094271,"uid":60338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"上個月條友仔浦過頭<br />\n28xxx個時又係到害人話開始跌市或回調<br />\n一個星期多D。284升到而加303<br />\n條友真係仲係到硬淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大佬就算比你講中。2019年11月先開始跌。升到33000先跌都害死人啦<br />\n你話27000開淡。每夾一千點加淡<br />\n唔係大戶邊有咁大個倉可以頂到33000呀。而加都3000點。係到引人話咩破左自己入場位33000就當輸。我屌睇到呢句真係火都黎。27000開到33000真係輸到跳樓。成日係到死撐唔食B浪只食C浪。唔食B浪咪比人夾至少3000點甚至升到33000，6000點呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />何況今年個勢似足完撚左熊市。根本似足牛一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=比沒事巴影響過唔敢開牛仲開過熊夾過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=2019年一直都無信過條仆街。26000已經開牛"},{"pid":"ba4a9d58d80d9b34bfb5a4ec9c12f92d5cc0a4e8","tid":1094271,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:02:17.000Z","msg":"唔好再牛熊啦...指數呢啲預測唔到"},{"pid":"14fd117dd4cacdf21ba21474d5e0a9b9e1dfb2d2","tid":1094271,"uid":52911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"希望比沒事兒呃到滿淡倉輸到要跳樓位巴打安息🙏🏻"},{"pid":"445277cf4a4de0d5207f10bf7349845b1ad90d8f","tid":1094271,"uid":131298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"支持鞭屍"},{"pid":"e0f646a6e2712ee84d0cd0c2b9ba719d3e94eeb8","tid":1094271,"uid":60338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"14fd117dd4cacdf21ba21474d5e0a9b9e1dfb2d2","tid":1094271,"uid":52911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:25:05.000Z","msg":"希望比沒事兒呃到滿淡倉輸到要跳樓位巴打安息🙏🏻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T09:27:09.000Z","msg":"好心沒事巴出黎認錯等班信徒咪再落淡